  "text": "In order to account for non-independence of observations (due to the fact that the participants were each part of a twin dyad), linear mixed-effect models with random intercept and Satterwhaite correction were used [CITATION_1] . The lme4 package was used to perform the analysis in R [CITATION_2] .",
